name: Magnetic Locket set - Click to see all designs
description:
**This item is shipped from the USA**

This adorable locket set was created in collaboration with Polarity Lockets™, and is made from a recycled steel auto part!

Each locket set includes 3 magnetic interchangeable lids, featuring my illustrations and a special word that ties them together. Simply choose one of the following sets from the drop down menu:
1.	Together locket set (1st image): This set features my ‘Human Nature’ & ‘Never Alone’ illustrations and the definition of the word ‘Together’.
2.	Bliss locket set (2nd image): This set features my ‘Happy Moment’ & ‘Bliss’ illustrations and the definition of the word ‘Bliss’.
3.	Whole Heart locket set (3rd image): This set features my ‘Healing’& ‘Complete’ illustrations and the definition of the word ‘Whole’. 

Your locket set comes on an adjustable length 30" 2mm nickel plated brass ballchain adorned with a beautiful rudraksha seed for good luck! Locket is 1 1/4". 

Just add your favorite little picture inside. Your locket is packaged in a cute little tin, perfect for gift giving or storage.

Your purchase will be wrapped with care and mailed in a nanosecond.

All Polarity jewelry including the changeable magnetic top is copyrighted 2008 - 2013 ; all designs used on the jewelry are copyrighted by Shira Sela.
